review: Best thing after reaching Dent-O-Health I experienced the simplicity of the clinic and the doctor. I was amazed by her explaining capability to a person who has zero knowledge on this field even over video consultation.What I liked most is the clarification made by Doctor. She did not advice anything more than required and made 100% clear about the expectations after the procedure. She listened through all the issues patiently and suggested the best can be done in current situation. I have not seen an iota of arrogance in her ** * **** *** ************* ******* She was being open to requests/suggestions from the patient. She always focused on long term cure of an issue. Her caring and down to earth nature easily creates a sense of trust on her.I have done my Mom's Flap surgery (gum treatment), 3 implant s, 1 Denture for my Grand Mom with a very reasonable price.
